      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters including blood viscosity, density, and hemolysis model coefficients must have quantified uncertainty distributions used in the Monte Carlo UQ at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed but hemolysis model coefficients were treated as fixed values rather than uncertain inputs. Input uncertainty characterization is incomplete for MRL 5. Flagged as epistemic gap."
    },
