      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples used for validation must be characterized for biological variability, with sufficient replicates to establish statistical confidence in measured hemolysis index values at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Test sample characterization was not assessed. The number of experimental replicates and biological variability in blood samples used for validation were not documented. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
