    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been reviewed under the ASME V&V 40 framework at Model Risk Level 5. Seven factors were formally assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels. Six factors remain not assessed, representing epistemic gaps that must be addressed before regulatory submission. The overall credibility assessment does not meet the threshold for acceptance at MRL 5 for a Class III VAD device. The package is structurally complete and the hash has been recorded for integrity tracking.",
